    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="操作系统"><a href="#操作系统" class="headerlink" title="操作系统"></a>操作系统</h1><h2 id="进程和线程"><a href="#进程和线程" class="headerlink" title="进程和线程"></a>进程和线程</h2><h3 id="基本概念"><a href="#基本概念" class="headerlink" title="基本概念"></a>基本概念</h3><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109191155712.png" alt="image-20201109191155712"></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109191445584.png" alt="image-20201109191445584"></p><h3 id="通信"><a href="#通信" class="headerlink" title="通信"></a>通信</h3><h4 id="进程间通信"><a href="#进程间通信" class="headerlink" title="进程间通信"></a>进程间通信</h4><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109193110806.png" alt="image-20201109193110806"></p><h4 id="线程间通信"><a href="#线程间通信" class="headerlink" title="线程间通信"></a>线程间通信</h4><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109193150619.png" alt="image-20201109193150619"></p><h3 id="线程间同步方式"><a href="#线程间同步方式" class="headerlink" title="线程间同步方式"></a>线程间同步方式</h3><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109205204925.png" alt="image-20201109205204925"></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109205225767.png" alt="image-20201109205225767"></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109205338684.png" alt="image-20201109205338684"></p><h3 id="有进程后为什么需要线程"><a href="#有进程后为什么需要线程" class="headerlink" title="有进程后为什么需要线程"></a>有进程后为什么需要线程</h3><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109202257244.png" alt="image-20201109202257244"></p><h3 id="单核机器上写多线程程序是否考虑要加锁？"><a href="#单核机器上写多线程程序是否考虑要加锁？" class="headerlink" title="单核机器上写多线程程序是否考虑要加锁？"></a>单核机器上写多线程程序是否考虑要加锁？</h3><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109202758437.png" alt="image-20201109202758437"></p><h3 id="线程需要保存哪些上下文，SP、PC、EAX这些寄存器是干嘛用的"><a href="#线程需要保存哪些上下文，SP、PC、EAX这些寄存器是干嘛用的" class="headerlink" title="线程需要保存哪些上下文，SP、PC、EAX这些寄存器是干嘛用的"></a>线程需要保存哪些上下文，SP、PC、EAX这些寄存器是干嘛用的</h3><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109203555248.png" alt="image-20201109203555248"></p><h3 id="多进程和多线程的使用场景"><a href="#多进程和多线程的使用场景" class="headerlink" title="多进程和多线程的使用场景"></a>多进程和多线程的使用场景</h3><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109210040475.png" alt="image-20201109210040475"></p><h3 id="常用的线程模型"><a href="#常用的线程模型" class="headerlink" title="常用的线程模型"></a>常用的线程模型</h3><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201121191323179.png" alt="image-20201121191323179"></p><h3 id="进程状态转换图"><a href="#进程状态转换图" class="headerlink" title="进程状态转换图"></a>进程状态转换图</h3><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201117203626402.png" alt="image-20201117203626402"></p><h2 id="并发和并行"><a href="#并发和并行" class="headerlink" title="并发和并行"></a>并发和并行</h2><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109200646789.png" alt="image-20201109200646789"></p><h2 id="Linux虚拟内存空间"><a href="#Linux虚拟内存空间" class="headerlink" title="Linux虚拟内存空间"></a>Linux虚拟内存空间</h2><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109194012989.png" alt="image-20201109194012989"></p><h3 id="虚拟内存置换的方式"><a href="#虚拟内存置换的方式" class="headerlink" title="虚拟内存置换的方式"></a>虚拟内存置换的方式</h3><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201117202019229.png" alt="image-20201117202019229"></p><h2 id="程序的内存结构"><a href="#程序的内存结构" class="headerlink" title="程序的内存结构"></a>程序的内存结构</h2><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109194703369.png" alt="image-20201109194703369"></p><h3 id="A-a-new-A-a-gt-i-10-在内核中的内存分配上发生了什么？"><a href="#A-a-new-A-a-gt-i-10-在内核中的内存分配上发生了什么？" class="headerlink" title="A* a = new A; a-&gt;i = 10; 在内核中的内存分配上发生了什么？"></a>A* a = new A; a-&gt;i = 10; 在内核中的内存分配上发生了什么？</h3><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201117204030799.png" alt="image-20201117204030799"></p><h3 id="静态变量什么时候初始化"><a href="#静态变量什么时候初始化" class="headerlink" title="静态变量什么时候初始化"></a>静态变量什么时候初始化</h3><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201121183457186.png" alt="image-20201121183457186"></p><h3 id="含有static，virtual等关键字的类的内存分布"><a href="#含有static，virtual等关键字的类的内存分布" class="headerlink" title="含有static，virtual等关键字的类的内存分布"></a>含有static，virtual等关键字的类的内存分布</h3><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201117205025664.png" alt="image-20201117205025664"></p><h2 id="缺页中断"><a href="#缺页中断" class="headerlink" title="缺页中断"></a>缺页中断</h2><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109195031920.png" alt="image-20201109195031920"> </p><h2 id="页表寻址"><a href="#页表寻址" class="headerlink" title="页表寻址"></a>页表寻址</h2><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109201834535.png" alt="image-20201109201834535"></p><h2 id="OS缺页置换算法"><a href="#OS缺页置换算法" class="headerlink" title="OS缺页置换算法"></a>OS缺页置换算法</h2><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109205808449.png" alt="image-20201109205808449"></p><h2 id="fork和vfork的区别"><a href="#fork和vfork的区别" class="headerlink" title="fork和vfork的区别"></a>fork和vfork的区别</h2><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109200021906.png" alt="image-20201109200021906"></p><h2 id="修改文件最大句柄数"><a href="#修改文件最大句柄数" class="headerlink" title="修改文件最大句柄数"></a>修改文件最大句柄数</h2><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109200413838.png" alt="image-20201109200413838"></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109200429238.png" alt="image-20201109200429238"></p><p><img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/SuzanneHuang/figurebed/master/img/image-20201109200455145.png" alt="image-20201109200455145"></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
