  <entry>
    <title>解决.sh: Permission denied</title>
    <link href="https://suzannehuang.github.io/2020/09/08/%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3-sh-Permission-denied/"/>
    <id>https://suzannehuang.github.io/2020/09/08/%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3-sh-Permission-denied/</id>
    <published>2020-09-08T08:23:36.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-09-08T08:47:15.517Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="背景"><a href="#背景" class="headerlink" title="背景"></a>背景</h3><p>在嵌入式系统想要在/cusdata目录执行脚本时发现该目录没有执行权限，会提示Permission denied</p><p>可是ls -l发现该目录和文件都是有执行权限的，查看/etc/scripts/mount_cusdata.sh发现</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mount -orw,,nosuid,nodev,noexec -t ext4 /dev/mmcblk0p23 /cusdata;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>系统给/cusdata分区挂载时加入了nosuid,nodev,noexec这些挂载选项（目的是为了提高linux系统安全性），所以导致即使在该目录让脚本可执行，实际还是不能执行。</p><h3 id="解决方法"><a href="#解决方法" class="headerlink" title="解决方法"></a>解决方法</h3><p> 编辑/etc/scripts/mount_cusdata.sh，去掉nosuid,nodev,noexec选项重启就ok了，还要注意关闭selinux，防止软链接之类的功能正常运转。</p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;h3 id=&quot;背景&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#背景&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;背景&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;背景&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;在嵌入式系统想要在/cusdata目录执行脚本时发现该目录没有执行权限，会提示Permission denied&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;可是ls -</summary>
      
    
    
    
    
    <category term="linux" scheme="https://suzannehuang.github.io/tags/linux/"/>
    
  </entry>
  
  <entry>
    <title>build asan for arm target</title>
    <link href="https://suzannehuang.github.io/2020/09/04/build-asan-for-arm-target/"/>
    <id>https://suzannehuang.github.io/2020/09/04/build-asan-for-arm-target/</id>
    <published>2020-09-04T13:29:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-09-14T09:26:10.875Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h3><p>由于应用在嵌入式设备运行的需要，尝试编译时加上asan，但是发现clang没有内置arm版本的asan库（libclang_rt.asan-arm.a等），所以需要自己编译。</p><h3 id="编译过程"><a href="#编译过程" class="headerlink" title="编译过程"></a>编译过程</h3><h4 id="下载源码"><a href="#下载源码" class="headerlink" title="下载源码"></a>下载源码</h4><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> <span class="built_in">cd</span> somewhere</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta">#</span><span class="bash"> Get llvm, clang and compiler-rt</span></span><br><span class="line">svn co http://llvm.org/svn/llvm-project/llvm/trunk llvm</span><br><span class="line">cd llvm</span><br><span class="line">R=$(svn info | grep Revision: | awk &#x27;&#123;print $2&#125;&#x27;)</span><br><span class="line">(cd tools &amp;&amp; svn co -r $R http://llvm.org/svn/llvm-project/cfe/trunk clang)</span><br><span class="line">(cd projects &amp;&amp; svn co -r $R http://llvm.org/svn/llvm-project/compiler-rt/trunk compiler-rt)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>To switch your checkout to read-write mode:</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">CNAME=your_name_here</span><br><span class="line">cd llvm</span><br><span class="line">svn switch --relocate http://llvm.org/svn/llvm-project/llvm/trunk https://$CNAME@llvm.org/svn/llvm-project/llvm/trunk</span><br><span class="line">(cd tools &amp;&amp; svn switch --relocate http://llvm.org/svn/llvm-project/cfe/trunk https://$CNAME@llvm.org/svn/llvm-project/cfe/trunk clang)</span><br><span class="line">(cd projects &amp;&amp; svn switch --relocate http://llvm.org/svn/llvm-project/compiler-rt/trunk https://$CNAME@llvm.org/svn/llvm-project/compiler-rt/trunk compiler-rt)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="交叉编译"><a href="#交叉编译" class="headerlink" title="交叉编译"></a>交叉编译</h4><p>首先进入源码里compiler-rt所在同级目录，创建asan_build目录。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cmake -DCOMPILER_RT_BUILD_BUILTINS=ON -DCOMPILER_RT_BUILD_SANITIZERS=ON -DCOMPILER_RT_BUILD_XRAY=ON -DCOMPILER_RT_BUILD_LIBFUZZER=ON -DCOMPILER_RT_BUILD_PROFILE=ON -DCMAKE_SYSROOT=/home/core/toolchain/arm-2019.09/arm-linux-gnueabi/libc/ -DCMAKE_C_COMPILER_EXTERNAL_TOOLCHAIN=/home/core/toolchain/arm-2019.09 -DCMAKE_ASM_COMPILER_TARGET=&quot;arm-linux-gnueabi&quot; -DCMAKE_C_COMPILER_TARGET=&quot;arm-linux-gnueabi&quot; -DCOMPILER_RT_DEFAULT_TARGET_ONLY=ON -DCMAKE_C_COMPILER=/home/core/toolchain/arm-2019.09/bin/arm-linux-gnueabi-gcc -DCMAKE_CXX_COMPILER=/home/core/toolchain/arm-2019.09/bin/arm-linux-gnueabi-g++ ../compiler-rt/</span><br><span class="line">make</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>编译成功，可以看到lib/linux/下有asan相关的库。</p><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">clang_rt.crtbegin-arm.o          libclang_rt.cfi-arm.a                libclang_rt.scudo_minimal-arm.so         libclang_rt.ubsan_standalone_cxx-arm.a</span><br><span class="line">clang_rt.crtend-arm.o            libclang_rt.cfi_diag-arm.a           libclang_rt.stats-arm.a                  libclang_rt.ubsan_standalone_cxx-arm.a.syms</span><br><span class="line">libclang_rt.asan-arm.a           libclang_rt.lsan-arm.a               libclang_rt.stats_client-arm.a           libclang_rt.xray-arm.a</span><br><span class="line">libclang_rt.asan-arm.a.syms      libclang_rt.profile-arm.a            libclang_rt.ubsan_minimal-arm.a          libclang_rt.xray-basic-arm.a</span><br><span class="line">libclang_rt.asan-arm.so          libclang_rt.scudo-arm.a              libclang_rt.ubsan_minimal-arm.a.syms     libclang_rt.xray-fdr-arm.a</span><br><span class="line">libclang_rt.asan_cxx-arm.a       libclang_rt.scudo-arm.so             libclang_rt.ubsan_minimal-arm.so         libclang_rt.xray-profiling-arm.a</span><br><span class="line">libclang_rt.asan_cxx-arm.a.syms  libclang_rt.scudo_cxx-arm.a          libclang_rt.ubsan_standalone-arm.a</span><br><span class="line">libclang_rt.asan-preinit-arm.a   libclang_rt.scudo_cxx_minimal-arm.a  libclang_rt.ubsan_standalone-arm.a.syms</span><br><span class="line">libclang_rt.builtins-arm.a       libclang_rt.scudo_minimal-arm.a      libclang_rt.ubsan_standalone-arm.so</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="参考链接"><a href="#参考链接" class="headerlink" title="参考链接"></a>参考链接</h3><p><a href="https://github.com/google/sanitizers/wiki/AddressSanitizerHowToBuild">https://github.com/google/sanitizers/wiki/AddressSanitizerHowToBuild</a></p><p><a href="https://llvm.org/docs/HowToCrossCompileBuiltinsOnArm.html">https://llvm.org/docs/HowToCrossCompileBuiltinsOnArm.html</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;h3 id=&quot;前言&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#前言&quot; class=&quot;headerlink&quot; title=&quot;前言&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;前言&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;由于应用在嵌入式设备运行的需要，尝试编译时加上asan，但是发现clang没有内置arm版本的asan库（libclang_rt.asan-</summary>
      
    
    
    
    
